{"tid":988960,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"「勸世」 其實賭錢真係100% 輸","createTime":"2019-01-20T13:29:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-20T15:54:15.000Z","uid":123335,"like":42,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"655abb4cca69cac0ec0949d7eb7b6561338d76ee","tid":988960,"uid":123335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T13:29:24.000Z","msg":"其實好多賭仔都心存僥倖<br />\n盲目以為自己好聰明<br />\n以為自己可以靠賭發達 <br />\n<br />\n坦白講<br />\n首先馬會同政府已經抽左總投注額既 2x % 既作為行政費<br />\n所以你就算贏<br />\n用simple maths 計下都知你個EV 係長期負數<br />\n數學上, 結論係馬會必贏, 賭仔長賭必輸 <br />\n<br />\n為左證實賭錢係必輸<br />\n我用少少錢黎買波 <br />\n俾大家一齊上一課教育課，從中汲取教訓<br />\n希望大家唔好再沉迷賭博 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XvoEDJq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXvoEDJq.jpg&h=1a333bb3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"56914547315c8014c75800ec45d775deae663d54","tid":988960,"uid":187108,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T13:29:57.000Z","msg":"彪哥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"434f484103ff78c7f7049990aaba139678b4b984","tid":988960,"uid":73241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T13:29:59.000Z","msg":"bill gor<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1e2d426493c00daa5685413a66c8c49474efdf8","tid":988960,"uid":34419,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T13:33:59.000Z","msg":"以身作則 教小朋友唔好賭錢 支持"},{"pid":"1e77b8ade2ae75956c9512e3e0edc5715b3fba5d","tid":988960,"uid":146193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T13:35:01.000Z","msg":"大陰燭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34222b8842daca59aee9f2c611c5468f94dd02d8","tid":988960,"uid":99700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T13:35:36.000Z","msg":"大陽具<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1077939ffbfce2c75538b29f4020f93c48cc4217","tid":988960,"uid":181378,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T13:41:08.000Z","msg":"真心，贏馬會既人一定有但係少數<br />\n我公司個阿叔中過六環彩贏600k<br />\n玩左廿年都係用馬會d錢對賭<br />\n要訣係少注刀仔鋸大樹，同埋用娛樂心態玩"},{"pid":"896b410ddb04dc0ee05e274b80290a010961be9a","tid":988960,"uid":31215,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T13:47:14.000Z","msg":"要賭贏馬會<br />\n你長賭必輪<br />\n個機率上賭仔蝕底<br />\n乜9必贏法都冇法<br />\n佢開得俾你賭，都係冇漏洞<br />\n<br />\n要贏<br />\n只有一個方法<br />\n就係賭一次，贏左之後永世唔再賭<br />\n<br />\n輸左就算<br />\n你條命冇得贏<br />\n再賭落去都係輸"},{"pid":"1a5c03e336bc57a676dafd90184cbbcd08538dcf","tid":988960,"uid":838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T14:08:23.000Z","msg":"本多終勝"},{"pid":"e9abf8c782a879c32a848d57e16f6b5a0909d652","tid":988960,"uid":59333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T14:10:55.000Z","msg":"一鍵留明"},{"pid":"0f0bea2bbe95988f09fb85611df87fc8ba89dea5","tid":988960,"uid":56097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T14:13:22.000Z","msg":"即場 等高水 角球同入球大細都可以有2倍跳船<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n所以狗會成撚日封盤 好驚"},{"pid":"bc078f9940e80eb25b4234aa7e708e8d46270f33","tid":988960,"uid":2692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T14:15:07.000Z","msg":"Lm"},{"pid":"4b5fd79f55ef0d0ce1549397f91c555e054c6c41","tid":988960,"uid":139720,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T14:20:34.000Z","msg":"賠率低唔等於一定輸"},{"pid":"58897ca85e48a1c3d8f00e57044475fc71b603f6","tid":988960,"uid":13503,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T15:17:30.000Z","msg":"受教了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd052c65835d222ba3ed09a1c56e73922138caed","tid":988960,"uid":46170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T15:19:07.000Z","msg":"幫馬會鋪草皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/nor